Package com.github._1c_syntax.bsl.parser

Interface SDBLParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
SDBLParserBaseListener
public interface SDBLParserListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by SDBLParser.
